subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: Aliy Zirkle, a three-time runner-up, surged to the lead of the Iditarod, but the four-time champion Jeff King and Aaron Burmeister were about two hours behind.
